                                <h2 class="h3 mr-3 mt-3">Basic examples</h2>
                            </div>
                            <p>By adding <code>data-countup</code> attribute you can initialise the component. There are a few available options, <code>data-from</code>, <code>data-to</code>, <code>data-decimals</code>, <code>data-duration</code> and <code>data-options</code> to add more options to your counter like prefix or suffix.</p>
                            <p class="font-italic text-muted font-size-5">Note: CountUp.js will only start counting when the user reaches the viewport!</p>

